# Classification-BRS-reports
# Code used for master thesis Information Science of the University of Groningen. 
# The code classifies BOA registrations in nine different classes, comparing one SVM, seven encoders and four decoders.
# Dutch-specific encoders: BERTje, Geotrend NL-BERT, RobBERT v2 and RobBERT v2 
# Multilingual encoders: mBERT, mDeBERTa v3 and XLM-RoBERTa 
# Dutch-specific decoders: Feitej-2b and GPT-2 Small Dutch
# Multilingual decoders: OPT-13B and Qwen2.5-0.5B
# The dataset is not publicly available
